data.description: Welcome to your new home, with a corner lot that exudes style from every corner and feels just like home. This residence offers spacious and well-appointed living spaces, providing comfort and privacy for every member of the household. Ascend the staircase to discover the charm of the upstairs balcony, offering panoramic views and a serene atmosphere for relaxation. The carefully designed layout includes a media room, perfect for entertainment enthusiasts and movie nights, as well as a versatile loft space. At the entrance of your home there is a private office space, ideal for those who seek a dedicated workspace or a quiet retreat. The thoughtful design extends outdoors to a large backyard, providing a canvas for your landscaping dreams and outdoor activities. Enjoy the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living with a covered patio that invites you to unwind and entertain in style.
